SecuredMe License Family

This repository defines two custom educational license texts:

- Secured Educational License 2.0: `LicenseRef-SEL-2.0`
- Secured Educational Cybersecurity License 2.0: `LicenseRef-SECL-2.0`

See:

- `LICENSE-SEL-2.0`
- `LICENSE-SECL-2.0`

Both license identifiers are custom `LicenseRef-*` identifiers. They are not
currently OSI-approved licenses and are not currently listed in the SPDX License
List. When using either identifier, include the full selected license text in
the target repository.

